- The server-side `IShipmentService` implementation is registered in server `Program.cs` and used during Server-side rendering.
- The client-side `IShipmentService` implementation is registered in client `Program.cs` and used during WebAssembly rendering.
- Make sure both `Program.cs` files register `IShipmentService` with their respective implementations.
- The track endpoint (`api/shipments/track/{trackingNumber}`) should be `AllowAnonymous` so unauthenticated customers can track shipments.
- The Home page tracking feature should work WITHOUT authentication.

